title: Windows KMS Activator Ultimate 2018 4.2 !{Latest}
description:
Windows KMS Activator Ultimate 2018 4.2 !{Latest}

Windows KMS Activator Ultimate 2018 is the most simple and user-friendly activator for Windows Vista, 7, 8, 8.1, 10, Office 2010/2013/2016 Preview.

 It is a safe activator, without harm to system files. The Windows activation period is 180 days, and you can renew it after its expiry.

You can delete all previous activations. You can find out information about your activation and the current activation status of your Windows.

Kms Activator can activate:
• Windows 10 all versions
• Windows 8.1 all versions
• Windows 8.1 Preview all versions
• Windows 8 all versions
• Windows 7 Professional
• Windows 7 Enterprise
• Windows Vista Business
• Windows Vista Enterprise
• Windows Server 12 all versions
• Windows Server 08 all versions

What's new:

-Add "Activation Digital License" tool latest version for permanent activation.
-Can activate the latest version of windows 10.
-Fixed For All Bugs
